creator: AliRadar Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Would you like to find out the truth about sellers and products on Ali? AliRadar app will help you to check the most helpful information:
- Seller trust level
- Product price history

The application collects data from AliExpress™ and gives clear recommendations about products, so that you can spend just a few seconds to make decision if the product is worth buying or if you should try another one.

Save the products to favorites to monitor the price changes. AliRadar will notify when the products become cheaper!
descriptionShort: Check sellers trust level and price history of products at Ali

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Just look at this new convenient navigation! “Hot products” are now always at hand, and soon there will be new awesome features🤘
For all questions and suggestions, please contact us at support@aliradar.com
